{"tid":144206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全國兩會】高鐵專家談一地兩檢：香港係中國一個省 誰不聽就滾","createTime":"2017-03-05T08:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T06:00:30.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"faaabfa3d73a4ff4d77fbd90fa715f68d0bc7b15","tid":144206,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"(更新內容)<br />\n<br />\n身兼全國人大代表的鐵路專家、中國工程院院士王夢恕被問及高鐵香港段一地兩檢安排仍然未落實，他炮轟港府未將設計權交予中央，令設計不單耽誤許多時間，而且設計費比內地貴一倍以上，故認為內地不可太嬌慣他們（香港）。<br />\n王夢恕講起香港高鐵語氣頗激動，認為香港段建造難度低，卻拖得時間長、成本高，是管理班子不力所致。「以前劉部長（指原鐵道部長劉志軍）的時候，高鐵穿過哪個省，其實都遇到一些阻力的，當時哪個局辦事不力，就把哪個撤掉。」王夢恕稱，中央不會允許香港段爛尾，「絕對要修通，修不修通不是由香港說了算的」。他認為可以考慮由內地出錢、派人建設，「沒有多少錢，中央今年一年的鐵路建設預算是8000億」。<br />\n內地記者再問如何解決一地兩檢，他稱:「以後都不用檢了，都是一個國家了。」他舉例說，以前進入深圳要邊防證，當時也有下車檢查、車上檢查幾種方案，但因為後來人流太大，二線關最後取消。<br />\n王夢恕再就高鐵一地兩檢的安排表示「鐵路要拉通，一帶一路要拉通」。王夢恕在場亦指內地對香港太嬌慣，指香港是中國一個省，沒有甚麼好說，誰不聽話就滾出去。"},{"pid":"f1e8ce9abf395e0eadac1fe1d0dd6b3e828824f7","tid":144206,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"錢就香港俾<br />\n事就大陸話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfa20d553dcf38a170f33e81b9deac2079e3449","tid":144206,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"支那廿年<br />\n香港玩完"},{"pid":"2483694196a5d12fc421bb041b9a7ac7e7c71d2c","tid":144206,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"係咪想學大馬驅逐新加坡先例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fc93d06069d997182e62a2fd067a7aa78d44f1","tid":144206,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，當自己係邊個<br />\nD EQ咁低同講野唔經大腦嘅人都可以做到院長屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b27a09334b7ace6f09e81b8d6fd93f7f9838495","tid":144206,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"言辭犀利  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但只是法盲一枚"},{"pid":"256b7a917bb11ed5427c6aa9509687cb7b1af97b","tid":144206,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"中國無法律可言"},{"pid":"b54a95a2a7838581d620fbe13c8a3be04a72c11a","tid":144206,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"真心愛國既人，係制度守護者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係班支國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb835f50afd3b9415607a248f9eec119111a2ff","tid":144206,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全個香港滾啦<br />\n<br />\n我唔介意獨立喎！</span>"},{"pid":"a19b92e11406591ee67f028f6f6fb883d020650a","tid":144206,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"把香港踢出中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57b5da335bbe7caa1164d3b1100448c05bc6fae","tid":144206,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"驅逐香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d5a568e0e96a33a25b3f1d6700cdacc82984e0","tid":144206,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:42:08.000Z","msg":"konexit<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ded6aa736e36e4b3926d3e4d865509c14fc872","tid":144206,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:54:47.000Z","msg":"獨立正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672dbf7ef936712b264a1bc5911aa4164